Job Description
Project EngineerWith Leading Offshore ContractorCompetitive RemunerationWorking closely with a leading offshore contractor, our client is expanding its installation team with the recruitment of a Project Engineer. Reporting to the Operations Manager, this position is Singapore-based and we are looking for someone with proven installation experience in shallow water Rigid Lay.As the Project Engineer, you are responsible for all technical execution activities inclusive but not limited to the following – planning, scheduling, coordinating and ensuring delivery within cost control. You will draw on extensive hands-on experience, especially in Southeast Asia operations, having held responsibilities in client interfacing, tendering and operations.You should have a strong degree in Engineering and excellent knowledge of offshore installation. This opportunity offers competitive remuneration and a platform to further your experience with high-profile projects in this region.If this sounds like an opportunity you are interested in, please contact Ambrose Chan at
